title:
http://www.thekitchn.com/how-to-make-classic-creamy-coleslaw-recipe-221093
http://www.seriouseats.com/2013/07/the-food-lab-how-to-make-the-best-creamy-cole-slaw.html

Dressing 1:
1 cup mayo
1/4 cup white wine vinegar or cider vinegar
1 tbsp sugar
1/2 tsp salt

Dressing 2:
1/2 cup mayo
1/2 cup sour cream
1/4 cup white wine vinegar or cider vinegar
1 tbsp sugar
1/2 tsp salt

Dressing 3:
1/2 cup mayo
1/2 cup buttermilk
1/4 cup white wine vinegar or cider vinegar
1 tbsp sugar
1/2 tsp salt

to fridge for 1hr
